      "content": "i mean i get that, but honestly the campus clinic is gonna be closed soon and i really can't afford to waste time/money on a doctor if it's just gonna be 'drink more water and rest'. plus it's actually feeling way better now, like the fog is lifting. i feel fine except for a little bit of stiffness in my neck. u dont think it's actually dangerous if the pain is already gone, right? i'll just take a double dose of ibuprofen and call it a night.",
